1 Nov 2007:
Ardb rebirth
Graham Smith takes Ardb project lead. 
Ardb is now hosted at googlecode.com. 
Graham and a brand new team takes over the task and will release 
soon a bug fix version, then start add new feature.

Keep in touch with Ardb-v2.0.

Cheers. The Ardb Team. 

26 Feb 2003:
wxWindows is officially adopted for ARDB, because of it's ease of use,
and awesome cross-platform features. 